description:
This style adjust some CSS values.
It is not perfect, but still works.

It also remove the number of notes in each tag. You can comment or remove 

.elementCount, elementePublicCount{
 display : none !important;
}

to not disable the original feature.

css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document domain("ubernote.com") {

#catpane{
 width : 175px !important;
} 
#noteside,.noteside{
 width : 1085px !important;
 left: 25px !important;
 right:0 !important;
/* padding: 30px 200px 0px 0px !important;*/
}
#topStatus{
 padding: 3px 10px 3px 3px !important;
}
.NoteText{
 padding: 10px 0px 10px 10px !important;
}
.elementCount, elementePublicCount{
 display : none !important;
}
}
